  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mmday11ijxg\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"800\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/cYfMwRADOvpBlkT02f23A6WWxRoaiavoQMzvD8mOUleYpK8lwHb1HyFBpnib0lqxwxOwFeduUfk2yau48iaVG7yuwa32RO11AsJKwN9UX4aWXE/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"546\" data-cropsely2=\"255\" data-backw=\"546\" data-backh=\"307\" data-imgfileid=\"503380218\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c129d8de&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FcYfMwRADOvpBlkT02f23A6WWxRoaiavoQMzvD8mOUleYpK8lwHb1HyFBpnib0lqxwxOwFeduUfk2yau48iaVG7yuwa32RO11AsJKwN9UX4aWXE%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mmday11ijxg\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mmdaz56kq3m\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mmdaz5681259\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">来源丨</span></span><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">亿邦动力</span></span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">（ID：</span></span><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">iebrun</span></span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">）</span></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mmday11ijxg\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mmdaz56kq3m\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mmdaz5681259\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">作者丨</span></span><em mpa-font-style=\"mme9rhtb1rmp\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;em&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;mpa-font-style&quot;:&quot;mme9rhtb1rmp&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-size: 15px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;strong&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">姜琪</span></span></strong></em></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mmday11ijxg\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mmdaz56kq3m\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mmdaz5681259\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">编辑丨</span></span><em mpa-font-style=\"mme9rhtbb3w\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;em&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;mpa-font-style&quot;:&quot;mme9rhtbb3w&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-size: 15px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;strong&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">董金鹏</span></span></strong></em></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mmday11ijxg\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mmdaz56kq3m\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mmdaz5681259\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">图源丨Mijourney</span></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mme9rhtb95o\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">十万成本，四天时间，换来亿级曝光。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mme9rhtbqbw\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">去年秋天，AI漫剧《洪荒：代管截教，忽悠出了一堆圣人》首播，爆了。89集，没有真人演员，没有实景拍摄，全部由算法逐帧生成，风格在动态漫画与动画之间。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mme9rhtb3ef\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">《洪荒》制作方是酱油文化，商务负责人叫颜四海，他觉得”这个行业好像产生了一个风口”。</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">投放开始一天只有20万，2025年底飙到2000万，2026年1月中旬过3000万。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mme9rhtbev3\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">颜四海说，这个市场变化非常快。2025年9月，酱油文化只能做几十部AI漫剧，三个月后直接攀升到200部，团队规模也从500快速扩充至近千人。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mme9rhtb1s8e\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">AI漫剧快速起量，极有可能正在复制短剧的路径。2025年11月，字节跳动旗下独立App红果漫剧上线，首月活跃用户854万；12月，百度旗下独立漫剧App柚漫剧上线。进入2026年，百度旗下七猫漫剧App上线，腾讯旗下火龙漫剧也悄然登场。</span></p>\n  <div data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <div>\n    <div>\n     <div>\n      <p style=\"margin:0px 16px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.711111111111111\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align:middle;max-width:100%;width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;\" data-backw=\"546\" data-backh=\"934\" data-imgfileid=\"503630632\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=26adca4b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FBvOXUE29CF3HuReT3WJbShmW1BrY0a2glrs7NUKgSC5RPVaYshclmAC8o74Lt2tN0fLLm0ia3gvbD5doqRnHLgWMzfcRgAX2L63tqmkx7Xn4%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mme9rhtb1fma\">成本被击穿，周期被压缩，产能被拉到极限，网文似乎找到它最暴利的影像化出口，所有人都想抢到百亿剧场的门票。根据媒体披露的数据，2025年漫剧市场规模168亿元，2026年预计将突破240亿元，涨幅45%。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 16px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.07777777777777778\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"900\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/03KNO9Fib2w5wrEGVRwwiaPQcjibpiahYT0zPEErlmM1icwAxnc0Bfu3icv2I49pcxADF7lYww8vNML5TkajhGu2m1NA/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-cropselx2=\"546\" data-cropsely2=\"162\" data-backw=\"546\" data-backh=\"42\" data-imgfileid=\"502705851\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d0e93a19&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F03KNO9Fib2w5wrEGVRwwiaPQcjibpiahYT0zPEErlmM1icwAxnc0Bfu3icv2I49pcxADF7lYww8vNML5TkajhGu2m1NA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mme9zn3mki5\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:20px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mme9zn41bit\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">比短剧更快</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mme9zn3mki5\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:20px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mme9zn41bit\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">有企业10倍薪资挖人</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mme9rhtbohd\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">程杜新，百度柚漫剧负责人，2023年底参与搭建百度短剧业务。那时，短剧正在全面爆发，尽管行业规模还在快速增长，但留给新玩家的空间已经不多。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mme9rhtbcw4\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">2025年，短剧进入减速校准期，漫剧爆火。程杜新觉得，两者路径非常相似，但漫剧显然更快。“从起量到现在，还是原来这波人、这波用户、这些平台，甚至是同一套商业变现模式，它们太像了。唯一区别是供给形态和生产方式发生了变化。”</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mme9rhtbl5r\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">程杜新觉得，漫剧是一个AI在C端真正能落地的场景，而非单纯内容风口。内容风口靠用户运营和赛道孵化，就像几年前小红书做户外和露营，慢慢养出一批新供给。但漫剧不一样，背后是AI对生产关系的重构，也是对成本结构的彻底改变。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mme9rhtb197\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">总之，AI漫剧是一门可以用技术杠杆撬动的生意。“所以我们判断，它的窗口期会很短，红利期也会很短。要么现在冲进去，要么就没机会了。”程杜新说。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mme9rhtb1che\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">这个判断直接决定了柚漫剧的执行速度。他们从核心架构里抽人，专攻AI漫剧。一支五六人的产品团队，从决定做独立漫剧App，再到产品上线，只用了一个多月。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mme9rhtbwcv\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">想拿到百亿剧场门票，玩家们就必须与时间赛跑。这不是渲染焦虑。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mme9rhtb1584\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">漫剧很吃版权，目前走在前面的是字节系产品，背靠番茄小说海量IP，用低成本内容快速铺量、数据试错和批量复制。其他大厂，腾讯手握阅文，爱奇艺有大量影视IP储备，B站有完整动画生态，七猫也在做漫剧App。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mme9rhtb9th\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">风口之下，玩家和资本也在大量涌入。除了上述内容平台，就连美团也在首页嵌入饭团漫社，打包了小说、视频和漫剧。一些爆款漫剧制作厂商也受到资本青睐，比如酱油文化得到阅文集团投资、灵漫快创拿到A股上市公司万兴科技投资。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mme9rhtbtf5\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">“平台陆续都在动，只是响应速度和战略决心不一样。”程杜新说。有相关人士称，上游版权方与平台流量方将成为漫剧行业竞争的核心变量，巨头入场快速推高买量成本，让中小玩家空间越来越小。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mme9rhtbyrp\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">这或许也是柚漫剧被推上前台的原因。作为百度在漫剧领域的布局，它则是内容形态持续演化过程中</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">，百度主动承接年轻用户注意力、完善内容生态闭环的重要一环。漫剧也正成为平台抢占用户时长、构建内容护城河的新阵地。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.66640625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"width: 100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"375\" data-imgfileid=\"503630634\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=36d97bc3&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FBvOXUE29CF0IunTscEBEViaiaQJ3l005icTQNzD4Iwib1JDeh3fJ2Ea6a3SicsPXwPTBz1HN7UYTFtc7vpnP1lTHWVhgCmRwEA0Lh9I3NjdtaibCI%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mme9rhtb1g8s\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mm9x3tzo1rft\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">巨头扎堆进场，也直接引爆了行业的“抢人潮”。AI漫剧的爆红，让一个全新的高薪工种——“抽卡师”应运而生。</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">他们用AI图像工具，反复</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">输入指令</span><span style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" leaf=\"\">（行话叫“抽卡”）</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">，生成符合剧情要求的角色、场景和动作，保证同一角色在不同镜头里保持一致。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mme9rhtbodr\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">事实上，不止抽卡师。从AI工作流设计师到复合型内容策划，市场对“既懂技术又懂内容”的人需求迫切。与整体就业市场的低迷形成反差的是，多家漫剧公司都在喊“招不到合适的人”。有企业为抢人，曾开出10倍薪资挖人。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 16px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.07777777777777778\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"900\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/03KNO9Fib2w5wrEGVRwwiaPQcjibpiahYT0zSsWdBUSJRaL8xxhHssPefRrhSRCKFFTvyO0oNl4HVrDTxA2PCXqv1g/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-cropselx2=\"546\" data-cropsely2=\"162\" data-backw=\"546\" data-backh=\"42\" data-imgfileid=\"502705850\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9f561975&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F03KNO9Fib2w5wrEGVRwwiaPQcjibpiahYT0zSsWdBUSJRaL8xxhHssPefRrhSRCKFFTvyO0oNl4HVrDTxA2PCXqv1g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mme9rhtby35\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:20px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mm9x4qu8jpr\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">出乎意外</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mme9rhtby35\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:20px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mm9x4qu8jpr\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">爆款都是年轻男性在刷</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mme9rhtbgw0\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">短剧，得女性者得天下。霸总、甜宠、虐恋，30-50岁女性情绪刚需，三年跑出近千亿规模。男性用户，通常被默认“难伺候”“不花钱”“只配看赘婿”。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mme9rhtb21fe\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">AI漫剧打破了上述共识。小李，00后男生，春节迷上AI末世剧，刷了整整一个假期。“看得我又怕又想看，春节放假熬夜都在看。”他的追剧清单，就包括《末日寒潮》《诡异末世》《极寒重生》等。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 16px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.57109375\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"width: 100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"321\" data-imgfileid=\"503630635\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=12540edb&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FBvOXUE29CF2g7qbNPJ8fVdZDwZspicfTcPyx1pqug5DXdVaOa16WZRaaNcniannicvIv2NZQaUcL9zy7iax2yiadIXVlNkzATtk2lTPbYYntABd8%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mme9rhtby8k\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mm9x5a021yay\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">仔细观察爆款漫剧，你会发现，80%以上是男频剧</span><span style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" leaf=\"\">（男生频道，主要面向男性观众）</span><span data-mpa-action-id=\"mm9x5f1s1omj\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">，题材集中在“三幻”</span><span style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" leaf=\"\">（玄幻、奇幻、魔幻）</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">以及系统流、异能、神豪等。它们的共同点是强冲突、强成长和强爽感。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mme9rhtb1trl\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">短剧与AI漫剧，为何会呈现出如此大的差别？</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mme9rhtb158n\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">行业人士称，主要跟制作成本和用户需求相关。在表现宏大玄幻场景时，真人剧的真实度和成本都非常高，而AI漫剧特效多、视觉冲击强，天然适合这些题材。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mme9rhtb152b\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">“重生”“开局”“系统”“末世”等高频词汇和剧情，也恰恰击中当下年轻男性的情绪痛点。主角永远能从废墟中站起，系统永远会在绝境中降临，漫剧为其提供了最低成本的代偿。男频网文那套玩法，无缝平移到了漫剧。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mme9rhtb22e1\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mm9x62uvoqm\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">《末日寒潮我有移动堡垒我怕谁》，典型的AI仿真人漫剧，剧情很简单</span><span style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" leaf=\"\">（极寒降临，主角开着移动堡垒，在末日里囤物资、收小弟、打丧尸）</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">，但爽点密集，节奏快，一集三四分钟，刷上停不下来。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mme9rhtb1k8y\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">这部漫剧上线当月，播放增量2.4亿，拿下抖音原生漫剧播放增量第一。用AI生成高度拟真的“演员”进行表演，被认为未来可能冲击真人短剧。2026年1月，AI仿真人漫剧在百强榜中占38席，总计播放量达25.48亿，上榜率从2025年的7%飙升至38%。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mme9rhtbmpq\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">多位从业者称，女频漫剧处于稀缺状态，被视为下一个增长点。尤其在AI真人漫技术逐步成熟后，其细腻的情感呈现与表情控制，被认为更适合女频题材的深度开发。据了解，市场上已有团队正将重心转向AI真人剧开发。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mme9rhtbz9d\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">根据某机构发布的数据，31-40岁漫剧用户占比31.81%，24-30岁占比24.04%，18-23岁占比23.07%。快手的数据也显示，漫剧与真人短剧付费用户重合率仅为38%。也就是说，漫剧能给行业带来62%的增量付费用户。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mme9rhtb1zp8\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">由此可见，尽管与短剧有许多相似之处，但AI漫剧的主力用户是一群年轻人，与短剧的“下沉女性”用户并不重叠。有投资人分析称，大厂入局，赌的不仅是当下的变现效率，还有下一代内容消费人群。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mme9rhtbx74\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mm9x6td31h63\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">漫剧与短剧最主要区别是生产方式和效率。一部真人短剧，成本普遍在40万-70万元，精品剧轻松破百万。一部100集的漫剧，成本可以控制在15万元以内。如果是PPT漫</span><span style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" leaf=\"\">（类似“有画面的小说”）</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">，几千到一两万元就能搞定；沙雕漫，用熊猫头表情包做角色，成本一万到数万元不等；真正主流的动态漫，成本也只有十万到二三十万元。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mme9rhtb18op\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">“传统动画制作，需要90天完成的动态漫，通过引入AI工具，可以压缩到10-13天。”酱油文化商务负责人颜四海称，压缩比例近90%。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mme9rhtb3yg\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">AI让成本断崖式下降，直接引爆了产能。巨量引擎数据显示，2025年上半年，漫剧剧目供给量月复合增长率高达83%，流水增长12倍。2025年9月单月，抖音平台上线漫剧超6500部，产能已逼近真人短剧。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 16px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.07777777777777778\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"900\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/03KNO9Fib2w5wrEGVRwwiaPQcjibpiahYT0zotCTF2kebByIao1mukeoCXNY3JU0WuJBsy2jtgbt4REff8WQwWR4oQ/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-cropselx2=\"546\" data-cropsely2=\"162\" data-imgfileid=\"502705852\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b2401e1e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F03KNO9Fib2w5wrEGVRwwiaPQcjibpiahYT0zotCTF2kebByIao1mukeoCXNY3JU0WuJBsy2jtgbt4REff8WQwWR4oQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mme9rhtb11gi\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:20px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mm9x7p1r1e3f\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">掘金之路</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mme9rhtb11gi\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:20px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mm9x7p1r1e3f\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">在漫剧可能迎来二次爆发？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mme9rhtb14kt\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">短剧走到今天，用了接近三年时间，漫剧大概半年就走完了。这主要得益于漫剧几乎完整继承了短剧的三大变现路径：即广告变现、应用内付费与平台分账。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mme9rhtbns8\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">根据亿邦动力调查，多元化变现给玩家带来可观回报。一位从业者称，他们单剧投广ROI超1.1，全域经营综合ROI超过1.8，已明显高于短剧约1.3+的综合ROI。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mme9rhtb1nqm\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">在柚漫剧平台，当前所有剧集均可以免费观看，未来收入模式可能也不会直接面向剧集收费，\"用户已经被免费模式教育的比较成熟，对泛娱乐类内容付费意愿并不高，免费模式又能跑得通，”程杜新说，“这已成为了行业共识。”</span></p>\n  <div data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <div>\n    <div>\n     <div>\n      <div>\n       <p style=\"margin:0px 16px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"2.012962962962963\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align:middle;max-width:100%;width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;\" data-backw=\"546\" data-backh=\"1099\" data-imgfileid=\"503630637\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=802560b7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FBvOXUE29CF2E5t0fhF0rJsYuITg1azicVjVyacTxsicRdwM273bwuic7hH2YZic58n1eCOHtLIWwE1RCHibEYYrnJ7DlXjj2wPQaYHnfF0YEiaFHI%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:12px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mmea0hvh1r5j\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mmea0hvv19mc\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">柚漫剧APP截图</span></span></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mme9rhtbga2\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">除了完全继承短剧的变现路径，漫剧爆发也是AI技术给的底气。从剧本、角色、场景、分镜到配音，AI已逐步渗透到漫剧创作的每一个关键节点。在成本端，AI技术正带来新的想象空间。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mme9rhtb1ciw\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">目前，漫剧制作有两条技术路径：</span></p>\n  <ul style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"color:#888888;\">\n    <p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mme9rhtb22wg\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">一条是端到端生成，创作者像使用Agent一样，通过对话式交互，依次完成剧本、分镜、画面和配音，由多个模型串联起全流程；</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"color:#888888;\">\n    <p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mme9rhtbgwi\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">一条是在垂直环节引入模型优化，用基础模型生成剧本，借助LoRA打造风格统一的角色。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mme9rhtb15ke\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">比如，《洪荒：代管截教，忽悠出了一堆圣人》制作方酱油文化，2025年初营收目标还是五六千万元，5月上调至亿元。该公司就拥有自己独特的画风，在声音层面则涉及TTS、BGM生成、人物配音等多个环节的模型介入。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mme9rhtb13pc\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">由于成本、周期和产能等优势，AI漫剧公司的业务规模和营收也在快速上涨。一些分析人士认为，如果趋势持续下去，用不了多久，影响必定会波及短剧。不过，也有分析认为，AI漫剧面临内容同质化严重和IP价值偏弱等问题。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mme9rhtb21u5\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mm9xaaxj1a9b\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">程杜新要乐观得多，认为漫剧未来有机会孵化出超级IP，并延展出虚拟角色、互动陪伴和衍生品等。“我们希望用户能在这里弥补‘意难平’。”他说。“未来的漫剧可能不再只是‘看’，而是像游戏一样，用户可以实时互动、选择剧情分支，甚至剧情由AI实时生成。它更像一种开放世界的探索体验，就像《塞尔达传说》</span><span style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" leaf=\"\">（任天堂企划制作本部开发、Monolith Soft协力开发的动作冒险游戏）</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">。”</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mme9rhtb9fk\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">快手漫剧负责人也认为，如果AIGC能实现工业级应用、大规模生产，那么短剧领域难以实现的题材和场景，在漫剧领域就可能迎来二次爆发。“所以我觉得它的窗口期和黄金期会更长，会随着技术迭代不断出现细分机会。”</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mme9rhtb4b1\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">如果说短剧提供的是即时爽感，那么由技术驱动的漫剧，未来可能提供的是持续陪伴。角色不再是屏幕中的幻影，而是一个可以随时对话、随时互动的存在。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mme9rhtbnb\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">这是漫剧的黄金时代，也是内容行业最躁动的时刻。所有人都想抢到通往下一个百亿的门票，但没人知道终点在哪里。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mme9rhtb1u51\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">唯一确定的是：当AI拧紧发条，这场狂奔才刚刚开始。</span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "AI 漫剧通过重构生产关系将制作成本降低 90%，正以年轻男性为核心受众，迅速复制并超越短剧的百亿级商业路径。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "AI 漫剧通过重构生产关系将制作成本降低 90%，正以年轻男性为核心受众，迅速复制并超越短剧的百亿级商业路径。",
  "summary": "本文深度调研了 AI 漫剧行业的爆发式现状。得益于 AIGC 技术对剧本、分镜、配音全流程的渗透，漫剧制作成本从真人短剧的数十万降至十万级，周期缩短近 90%。与短剧“下沉女性”受众不同，AI 漫剧凭借玄幻、末世等题材吸引了大量年轻男性，带来了 62% 的增量付费用户。目前，字节、百度、腾讯等大厂已悉数入场，通过独立 App 争夺版权与流量红利，行业正从单纯的内容风口转向技术驱动的 C 端落地场景。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "AI 技术实现了内容生产成本的断崖式下降与产能爆发。",
      "explanation": "通过引入 AI 工作流，传统动画 90 天的制作周期被压缩至 10 天左右，成本仅为真人短剧的四分之一，极大地提升了试错效率。"
    },
    {
      "point": "AI 漫剧成功开拓了年轻男性受众这一内容消费增量市场。",
      "explanation": "80% 以上的爆款为男频题材，满足了年轻男性对玄幻、爽感的代偿需求，与传统短剧用户重合率仅 38%，展现了极强的吸金能力。"
    },
    {
      "point": "行业竞争核心已转向版权储备、流量分发与 AI 工业化能力。",
      "explanation": "大厂入局推高了买量成本，拥有海量网文 IP 的平台更具优势；未来漫剧将向虚拟角色互动、实时生成等更深度的 AI 场景演进。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
